Q

qclass - Variable in class com.zorben.dns.message.MessageQuestion
A two octet code that specifies the class of the query.
qdcount - Variable in class com.zorben.dns.message.MessageHeader
An unsigned 16 bit integer specifying the number of entries in the MessageQuestion section.
qname - Variable in class com.zorben.dns.message.MessageQuestion
A domain name represented as a sequence of labels, where each label consists of a length octet followed by that number of octets.
qr - Variable in class com.zorben.dns.message.MessageHeader
A one bit field that specifies whether this message is a query (0), or a response (1).
qtype - Variable in class com.zorben.dns.message.MessageQuestion
A two octet (byte) code which specifies the type of the query.
questions - Variable in class com.zorben.dns.message.Message
The MessageQuestion section contains fields that describe a question to a name server.
